    <h3>NSW Design System base colour theme</h3>
    <p>The Design System base colour theme is based on Level 01 colour usage rules which area applicable for Masterbrand Level 1 and 2 (L1/2). </p>

    <h4>Brand colours</h4>
    <p>Level 01 colour usage reflects a strong association to NSW Government through its use of the red, blue and grey colour sets. </p>
    <p>Foundations and components inherit Brand colours from the base colour theme and their individual guidance will explore the level of customisation or adaptation for each.</p>
